uclogic-tools
------------------------------------------
Uclogic-tools is a collection of programs for collecting and analyzing
diagnostic information from UC-Logic graphics tablets (rebranded as Huion,
Yiynova, Ugee, Monoprice, Turcom and others).

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libusb1.0-1.0.21-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-3
  automake-20250528-1
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-14.4.0-1
  libusb1.0-devel-1.0.21-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/DIGImend/uclogic-tools

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/DIGImend/uclogic-tools/archive/refs/tags/v5.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack uclogic-tools-5-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./uclogic-tools-5-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/uclogic-tools-5-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/uclogic-tools-5-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(uclogic-tools)
  /usr/bin/uclogic-decode.exe
  /usr/bin/uclogic-probe.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/uclogic-tools.README
  /usr/share/doc/uclogic-tools/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/uclogic-tools/README.md

